The paper deals with an optimization problem involving matroids and submodular functions, which are topics in discrete mathematics and theoretical computer science. The problem is also related to online algorithms and set cover, which are topics in algorithms and data structures. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IT (Information Theory).
